    <Folder id="236">
      <name>Tiber Upstream - Head of the Charles</name>
      <open>1</open>
      <description>rownative.icu
11 km practice course above the dam on the River Tiber

Boston's fall classic on the Charles River. Held in October - 3.2 mile course.</description>
